    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to drive away in a truly exceptional vehicle that looks and feels brand new! This car is in pristine, mint condition, meticulously cared for and showing no signs of wear inside or out. It\u2019s a rare find that offers a flawless driving experience and a showroom-quality finish that will turn heads wherever you go. This is the perfect opportunity to own a top-tier vehicle that has been maintained to the highest standards!",
