    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently requires significant mechanical attention, as the engine runs roughly and the transmission is showing signs of failure. The body has multiple dents and clear coat peeling, while the interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the upholstery. This would be an ideal project for a mechanic or someone looking for a parts car, as it will need a trailer to be moved safely.",
